8:
Oh, I don't know about that. Kind of 
hard to betray you when you've 
already made it clearâ€”you're no friend 
of the droids. You're no one's friend but 
your own.
11:
Sit tight in the Room of Idols. Justice 
will be coming along soon.
14:
Now, Nimbus. If you would do the 
honors?
23:
That wasn't an orderâ€”it was a request. 
Which, may I add, you accepted 
without hesitation.
28: Did we beat her? Like, for good?
32: Oh, no. That was just her terminal.
34:
But it had firepower, didn't it? You lot 
did very well to defeat it.
38:
"You lot did very well..." my exhaust 
pipes!
43:
Regis, you have two seconds to explain 
yourself before I personally rip your 
head off and silence you forever!
46: Whoa, easy there. I have my reasons...
55: Well... in so many words, yes.
56:
My goal is to topple the 
Administrator's throne. I've been 
working towards it for a while nowâ€”
long before I met you, or Dia even.
62:
Then why'd you try to get them 
captured?!
65:
I had to keep my guise up. If I didn't 
report them then and there, she'd 
have smelled a rat.
66:
And I figured their gig was up 
anyways! Leaping out in front of 
security like that... I was so scared, 
I started sweating through pores 
I don't even have!
69:
Plus, well... To tell the truth, I wanted to 
see how Light and co. would fare 
against her.
75:
You'd make one heck of an evil 
mastermind.
78:
Yes, well, thanks to your kind 
cooperation, I've managed to gather 
all my winning cards.
84: Those charming little bugs over thereâ€¦
88:
And the lovely angel that unites them all...
Stella.
96:
Now look here, princess. How long are 
you going to keep giving me the cold 
treatment?
102:
Well, don't you want to know all about 
what I've been doing, and my grand 
plan that's about to unfold?
108:
Ooh. I think I might just wither.
Well, since they're so vital to our 
daring mission, I think I'll tell you a 
thing or two about bugs anyways.
111:
Do you folks know what bugs really 
are?
116: Cut the crap and give it to us straight.
119:
Settle down, Nimbus. Patience is 
a virtue, you know.
121:
Bugs are the physical embodiment of 
wiped memories.
128:
There've always been droids who've 
bucked under the yoke of the 
Administrator. Oh, I couldn't tell you 
the number of minds she's hollowed 
out until now.
130:
And the memories, they're left out to 
rot, festering in a half-forgotten 
corner.
136: They kind of sound like ghosts...
138:
My old compatriotsâ€”and even the me 
of the pastâ€”are among that horde. 
Buzzing, angry, and set on getting 
even.
140:
Bugs exist to do one thing and one 
thing onlyâ€”bring the system of our 
dear creator crashing down on her 
head.
144:
Hah. They don't SOUND like ghosts, Alk. 
They ARE ghosts.
Guess it doesn't matter what world 
you're on. Old grudges die hard.
147:
But for all their fury, all their 
determination, bugs are small and 
a disorganized lot. I was never sure if 
they could draw near the tyrant 
herself.
148: That is, until I met Stella.
153: Stella... Can you really control bugs?
157:
Earlier, I heard a voice in my head. 
It kept repeating, "Pay. Pay for what 
you've done."
158:
Afterwards, my mind was filled with 
nothing but pain and hate and a thirst 
for vengeance...
160:
I don't know who was doing the 
controllingâ€”me... or the bugs.
163:
Yes, well, if we take the philosophy out 
of it and just state bald facts... Earlier, 
you gave an order, and the bugs 
listened.
164:
All I want you to do, Stella, is try. Just 
walk up to her with your buzzing army 
and say, "Now!" That's it.
169:
All this time, Regis... you were planning 
to take down the Administrator...
174:
Yes! You understand now, don't you, 
Dia? I was FORCED to act the way I did.
177:
Is that why you helped me be a singer? 
To get closer to her?
181:
Oh. Yes, well... I can't deny that that 
played a small role... but it's really not 
the whole story...
184:
It's okay, Regis... I don't need your 
excuses. I just wanted to know.
188:
We're here. The Room of Idols is just 
a few steps away.
192:
I'm certain she's prepared a warm 
welcome for us. En garde, 
compatriots!
